  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987630/extras/33fadbc1d59aae417a76519adf5c8cd7.avif?t=1643383255\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Whatever you mine - coal or diamonds - it all starts with opencast digging. And it's much more difficult as it would seem at first glance! Will you be able to complete this task?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987630/extras/6c95f3c175e259927dfeef3374165181.avif?t=1643383255\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>Place your personnel, buy new equipment and monitor the progress of work to level up your facility and be successful in mining.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987630/extras/dc56d04d0ba811a0a961ae6e00887676.avif?t=1643383255\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 10 various opencasts;<br></li><li>About 20 types of mining equipment;<br></li><li>Minimalistic low-poly design;<br></li><li>Several levels with increasing difficulty.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987630/extras/d90e140b9d76144c20b7ad983e60758d.webp?t=1643383255\" width=600 height=56 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987630/extras/33fadbc1d59aae417a76519adf5c8cd7.avif?t=1643383255\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Whatever you mine - coal or diamonds - it all starts with opencast digging. And it's much more difficult as it would seem at first glance! Will you be able to complete this task?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987630/extras/6c95f3c175e259927dfeef3374165181.avif?t=1643383255\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>Place your personnel, buy new equipment and monitor the progress of work to level up your facility and be successful in mining.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987630/extras/dc56d04d0ba811a0a961ae6e00887676.avif?t=1643383255\" width=600 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 10 various opencasts;<br></li><li>About 20 types of mining equipment;<br></li><li>Minimalistic low-poly design;<br></li><li>Several levels with increasing difficulty.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/987630/extras/d90e140b9d76144c20b7ad983e60758d.webp?t=1643383255\" width=600 height=56 /></span>",
